spec.collapsedText: "The iPhone 13 Pro is Apple's smaller premium iPhone with a 6.1" screen size and for the first time in an iPhone, it comes with a 120Hz ProMotion display for super smooth scrolling. The list of innovations includes a more capable triple camera setup, with a wide, ultra-wide and zoom cameras, as well as a LiDAR scanner.
